          },
          "reviewBody": "After lock down we were looking school for our child.\nFinalized  a good reputed school  near by our location.\nMy child got admission in UKG.\nThen we realized our child was under pressure,as he was not matching the reading, writing skill of his Class mates.\nTeacher were suggesting to repeat the same Class ,after new session.\nThen we start looking for new school   and find moslty 90% school have  same syllabus study pattern.\nAfter  some search we find Blue bell school sec 50.\nWe  discussed our problem with attending teacher (poonam mam) .She explain their teaching methodology.\nThey focus on each and every child.\nTo our satisfaction my child has shown remarkable growth in each subject  at the end of Grade 1 session .My child enjoyed each day in his new school",
